          "title": "Solo: A Star Wars Story",
          "year": 2018,
          "note": "Ehrenreich is fine, which is the whole problem when the role is Harrison Ford. Donald Glover's Lando is the through-line success; the Chewbacca meet-cute and the 10-minute war-movie detour work too. The knocks: a card game whose stakes you can't read, a Darth Maul cameo that raises more questions than it answers, and direction that's more competent than distinctive."
